abstract: Djamel Eddine Mesbah (Arabic: جمال الدين مصباح‎; born 9 October 1984 in Zighoud Youcef) is an Algerian professional footballer who plays as a left back for the Italian Serie A club Livorno on loan from Parma.An Algerian international, Mesbah was a member of the Algeria national team at the 2010 FIFA World Cup and the 2013 Africa Cup of Nations, both in South Africa.
